&quot;Based on the Austrian musical of the same name, this show traces the life of Elisabeth, empress of the Austrian Empire. Told through the eyes of her assassin, the Italian terrorist Luigi Lucheni, it follows Elisabeth from her impetuous, tom-boyish youth, through her falling in love and marrying the young Emperor Franz-Joseph, to her struggles with her strict mother-in-law, disillusionment in her husband, children, and eventual old age. Of course, this musical has a twist, for Death is also a constant watcher in Elisabeth's life, in love with her since she was a child and determined to make her love him in return....&quot;


